ComicInfo.Title: ТРИНА ДЦАТБ
ComicInfo.Summary:
New cover artist J.G. Jones (Black Widow) makes his debut in an issue focusing on Void! Learn the secrets of Void's recent and distant past and her human connection, and experience the surreal nature of a life lived between dimensions as we take a mental journey with a being whose powers often defy description.
